package model
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    WordleAccount
    An account that a user can login to to play Wordle.
    WordleBoard
    WordleBoard allows for one game of Wordle to be played.
    WordleGame
    Coordinates a game of wordle, keeping track of guesses, accounts, and whether or not the game is over.
    WordleWord
    An instance of WordleWord contains a five letter word which can be compared to another five letter word.
